message.body: Hey Liza are you decorating for psych's April Fools things?
Apparently? Our email thread just started up
Oh okay-- I was wondering if I could get a lift to staples sometime today since everything will be closed tomorrow for Easter and I haven't had any luck with people in the Chem dept
Ohhh ok well we don't have a plan yet so I have no idea what we are doing or who is going where when...
Ah I see. Good Luck!! and just so you know the party supply shop in Ardmore closes at 6 and the Staples closes at 9 tonight
Dhxgkvfxcj okay thanks. I guess we will figure it out somehow?
Yeah. This holiday thing threw us off too!!
